goombaAI : World -> Denizen -> Denizen
goombaAI w e = if (blockedX w {e|x <- e.x+e.dir}) then {e| dir <- (-e.dir), vx <- (-e.dir / 2)} else {e|vx<-(e.dir/2)}

defaultGoomba = {x=-16,y=0,vx=-0.5, vy=0, dir=-1, jumpEnergy=0, w=16, h=16}

